.B \-R
Run
.IR \%@g@refer (@MAN1EXT@)
preprocessor.
.
No mechanism is provided for passing arguments to
.I \%@g@refer
because most
.I \%@g@refer
options have equivalent language elements that can be specified within
the document.
.
See
.IR \%@g@refer (@MAN1EXT@)
for more details.
.
.
.TP
.B \-s
Run
.IR \%@g@soelim (@MAN1EXT@)
preprocessor.
.
.
.TP
