This sets the default
.B Print
action and the corresponding menu entry to that value.
.
.B \-X
produces good results only with
.BR \-Tps ,
.BR \-TX75 ,
.BR \-TX75\-12 ,
.BR \-TX100 ,
and
.BR \-TX100\-12 .
